+/**
+ * Master list of all components.
+ * 
+ * In the context of Access Control, "component" is used as a generic term for
+ * anything that can have its access restricted. High level concepts like
+ * Resources, Features, Applications, and Services are all categorized as
+ * components within the Access Control layer.
+ */
